<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Gift Aza Business Account Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h1 {
        color: #333333;
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      p {
        color: #555555;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .otp-container {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 6px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      .otp-code {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #8246f3;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #8246f3;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 3px;
        transition: all 500ms;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #8246f3;
        color: white;
        transform: scale(0.9);
      }

      .signature {
        color: #777777;
        font-style: italic;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Dear <%= name %>!</h1>
      <p>Thank you for signing up on Gift Aza</p>

      <div>
        <p>
          Please verify that your business email address is
          <b style="color: #8246f3"><%= email %></b>, and that you entered it
          when signing up on Gift Aza.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="otp-container">
        <p>Your One-Time Password (OTP) is:</p>
        <p class="otp-code"><%= OTP %></p>
      </div>

      <p>You can use the above OTP to verify your account.</p>

      <p>
        Kindly use this link to return to the page so you can proceed with your
        registration
      </p>
      <a href="http://localhost:5173/otp_vertification" class="button"
        >Continue Registration!</a
      >

      <p>
        With the app, users can browse through a selection of gift cards from
        top brands, purchase them with just a few taps, and send them to friends
        and family with personalized messages.
      </p>

      <p class="signature">Best regards,<br />Gift Aza Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
